file.name: schemas-test.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
paths:
  /ko-response-not-object:
    get:
      description: Test response not object
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
  /ok-response-is-object:
    get:
      description: Test response is object
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  foo:
                    type: string
        "201":
          description: Created
          content:
            application/v.foobar+json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/JsonObject"
          
  /ko-response-is-string:
    get:
      description: Test response is string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ko_String'
  /ok-skip-other-mediatypes:
    get:
      description: Test skip other mediatypes
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/pdf:
              schema:
                type: string
                format: bytes
  /ok-skip-patch-mediatype:
    get:
      description: Test skip other mediatypes
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            "application/json-patch+json":
              schema:
                type: array
                maxItems: 10
                minItems: 1
                items: {}
components:
  schemas:
    ko_String:
      type: string
    JsonObject:
        properties:
          foo:
            type: string
info:
  title: Test
  version: 1.0.0
